[
    {
        "text": "It's 7:00 a.m.",
        "start": 10.58,
        "duration": 1.14
    },
    {
        "text": "somewhere in the middle of Mauritania,",
        "start": 12.38,
        "duration": 2.369
    },
    {
        "text": "somewhere just on the edge of the Sahara",
        "start": 15.23,
        "duration": 1.769
    },
    {
        "text": "Desert, it's still dark outside.",
        "start": 17.0,
        "duration": 1.89
    },
    {
        "text": "I've been up since 4:00 a.m.",
        "start": 19.52,
        "duration": 1.372
    },
    {
        "text": "after about four hours of sleep because",
        "start": 21.35,
        "duration": 1.889
    },
    {
        "text": "I went to a wedding last night.",
        "start": 23.66,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "And right now, we're sitting here,",
        "start": 35.6,
        "duration": 2.519
    },
    {
        "text": "lying here, in fact, hey Mike",
        "start": 38.72,
        "duration": 1.949
    },
    {
        "text": "Hi!",
        "start": 41.45,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "waiting for a bus, apparently",
        "start": 44.03,
        "duration": 2.879
    },
    {
        "text": "that should take us to the starting point",
        "start": 47.33,
        "duration": 2.37
    },
    {
        "text": "of the roughest train ride",
        "start": 50.24,
        "duration": 2.4
    },
    {
        "text": "of our lives.",
        "start": 53.12,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "What is it in human nature",
        "start": 54.98,
        "duration": 2.037
    },
    {
        "text": "that would make someone spend 24 hours",
        "start": 57.342,
        "duration": 2.281
    },
    {
        "text": "on top of an exposed cargo train",
        "start": 59.623,
        "duration": 2.057
    },
    {
        "text": "speeding across the Sahara Desert?",
        "start": 61.68,
        "duration": 1.701
    },
    {
        "text": "I guess that's a question I'm seeking an",
        "start": 64.68,
        "duration": 2.069
    },
    {
        "text": "answer to as well.",
        "start": 66.749,
        "duration": 1.419
    },
    {
        "text": "We're sitting in a pretty crowded bus,",
        "start": 71.97,
        "duration": 1.949
    },
    {
        "text": "the gentleman behind me asked me to put on a hijab  ",
        "start": 74.37,
        "duration": 2.324
    },
    {
        "text": "and we're on our way to Zouerat",
        "start": 78.863,
        "duration": 2.399
    },
    {
        "text": "Two hours late",
        "start": 82.99,
        "duration": 1.369
    },
    {
        "text": "let's see if we can even catch the train today",
        "start": 85.33,
        "duration": 1.976
    },
    {
        "text": "This is not the train, ",
        "start": 91.48,
        "duration": 1.686
    },
    {
        "text": "this is a washroom, this is a toilet",
        "start": 93.471,
        "duration": 2.149
    },
    {
        "text": "in a tiny little town before Zouerat",
        "start": 96.46,
        "duration": 1.943
    },
    {
        "text": "I needed get out and use the washroom, ",
        "start": 98.483,
        "duration": 1.756
    },
    {
        "text": "but there wasn't one anywhere here, ",
        "start": 100.27,
        "duration": 1.666
    },
    {
        "text": "so a family let me into their house ",
        "start": 102.76,
        "duration": 1.435
    },
    {
        "text": "to use their bathroom. ",
        "start": 104.64,
        "duration": 0.806
    },
    {
        "text": "And this is how it looks.",
        "start": 105.446,
        "duration": 0.71
    },
    {
        "text": "This is the toilet and this is the water",
        "start": 106.9,
        "duration": 2.339
    },
    {
        "text": "that you  use to clean yourself.",
        "start": 109.24,
        "duration": 1.71
    },
    {
        "text": "This is the door.",
        "start": 111.07,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "The window.",
        "start": 112.21,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "The courtyard.",
        "start": 113.88,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "That is the little girl who brought me here.",
        "start": 116.63,
        "duration": 2.45
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm gonna switch off the camera now.",
        "start": 121.62,
        "duration": 1.14
    },
    {
        "text": "We finally arrived in the city",
        "start": 137.23,
        "duration": 2.639
    },
    {
        "text": "town of Zouerat",
        "start": 140.41,
        "duration": 1.708
    },
    {
        "text": "It looks like this.",
        "start": 142.75,
        "duration": 1.25
    },
    {
        "text": "now waiting for a taxi, which our",
        "start": 145.75,
        "duration": 1.889
    },
    {
        "text": "kind bus driver ordered for us",
        "start": 148.37,
        "duration": 1.472
    },
    {
        "text": "to take us to the train. ",
        "start": 150.73,
        "duration": 0.869
    },
    {
        "text": "Hopefully we're on time.",
        "start": 151.599,
        "duration": 1.545
    },
    {
        "text": "I should also add this comes in really,",
        "start": 153.22,
        "duration": 2.759
    },
    {
        "text": "really handy while travelling around",
        "start": 155.98,
        "duration": 1.764
    },
    {
        "text": "Mauritania. Our passports were checked",
        "start": 157.84,
        "duration": 2.069
    },
    {
        "text": "I think six times ",
        "start": 160.12,
        "duration": 1.386
    },
    {
        "text": "just on this one stretch of the journey.",
        "start": 161.642,
        "duration": 2.438
    },
    {
        "text": "Time for adventure!",
        "start": 166.03,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "That was actually our train",
        "start": 195.28,
        "duration": 1.555
    },
    {
        "text": "but for some reason ",
        "start": 196.835,
        "duration": 0.913
    },
    {
        "text": "we are now in the passenger carriage, ",
        "start": 197.748,
        "duration": 1.828
    },
    {
        "text": "just temporarily to sort out our stuff ",
        "start": 199.576,
        "duration": 2.227
    },
    {
        "text": "and then go to the real thing.",
        "start": 202.032,
        "duration": 3.368
    },
    {
        "text": "I don't know where it's gone ",
        "start": 206.11,
        "duration": 1.248
    },
    {
        "text": "Just passed us at a pretty high speed",
        "start": 207.671,
        "duration": 2.329
    },
    {
        "text": "What's the plan?",
        "start": 210.523,
        "duration": 1.222
    },
    {
        "text": "we don't know.",
        "start": 211.99,
        "duration": 0.809
    },
    {
        "text": "I think we move a bit and then we connect.",
        "start": 212.8,
        "duration": 1.38
    },
    {
        "text": "Then we we jump quick.",
        "start": 214.23,
        "duration": 1.078
    },
    {
        "text": "We hop on to it?",
        "start": 215.47,
        "duration": 0.988
    },
    {
        "text": "Jump quick? Hop on?",
        "start": 216.458,
        "duration": 1.142
    },
    {
        "text": "But as you can tell, it's not",
        "start": 217.6,
        "duration": 1.289
    },
    {
        "text": "OK.",
        "start": 221.26,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "We were just rushed out of the passenger car.",
        "start": 226.51,
        "duration": 1.95
    },
    {
        "text": "The gentleman here is taking us to the... ",
        "start": 228.91,
        "duration": 1.911
    },
    {
        "text": "The mineral wagons ",
        "start": 239.35,
        "duration": 1.585
    },
    {
        "text": "are the ones that carry the iron ore. ",
        "start": 240.935,
        "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
        "text": "They're just right up ahead",
        "start": 242.788,
        "duration": 2.099
    },
    {
        "text": "The train is moving, ",
        "start": 264.55,
        "duration": 1.506
    },
    {
        "text": "we are on it, ",
        "start": 266.571,
        "duration": 1.558
    },
    {
        "text": "and there's iron ore everywhere.",
        "start": 268.375,
        "duration": 2.315
    },
    {
        "text": "There's black dust everywhere.",
        "start": 270.74,
        "duration": 1.26
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh my God, we're in the middle of Mauritania",
        "start": 272.63,
        "duration": 3.128
    },
    {
        "text": "on an iron ore train",
        "start": 276.0,
        "duration": 2.73
    },
    {
        "text": "crossing the Sahara Desert",
        "start": 279.19,
        "duration": 1.951
    },
    {
        "text": " in the night!",
        "start": 281.141,
        "duration": 0.769
    },
    {
        "text": "What am I doing??",
        "start": 282.322,
        "duration": 1.588
    },
    {
        "text": "What am I doing, Mike?",
        "start": 283.91,
        "duration": 1.509
    },
    {
        "text": "This was only the beginning ",
        "start": 295.935,
        "duration": 1.254
    },
    {
        "text": "of a very long journey.",
        "start": 297.189,
        "duration": 1.462
    },
    {
        "text": "I know it all seems completely crazy ",
        "start": 299.063,
        "duration": 2.285
    },
    {
        "text": "but we tried to prepare as much as possible.",
        "start": 301.348,
        "duration": 2.174
    },
    {
        "text": "In an environment as harsh as this, ",
        "start": 304.377,
        "duration": 2.247
    },
    {
        "text": "you need to find ways to protect ",
        "start": 306.624,
        "duration": 1.398
    },
    {
        "text": "your frail little human body  ",
        "start": 308.022,
        "duration": 1.964
    },
    {
        "text": "from all the elements that surround you.",
        "start": 309.986,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "My God",
        "start": 322.48,
        "duration": 1.342
    },
    {
        "text": "these jolts are so powerful ",
        "start": 324.36,
        "duration": 1.687
    },
    {
        "text": "(Mike) Just 20 hours to go",
        "start": 326.047,
        "duration": 0.849
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh, there it is.",
        "start": 327.64,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "You OK? ",
        "start": 329.38,
        "duration": 0.62
    },
    {
        "text": "It's like the train is gurgling",
        "start": 336.04,
        "duration": 2.039
    },
    {
        "text": "all these weird, primordial noises happening, ",
        "start": 338.526,
        "duration": 2.548
    },
    {
        "text": "taking place, the train is moving ",
        "start": 341.074,
        "duration": 2.259
    },
    {
        "text": "back and forth, vibrating,",
        "start": 343.333,
        "duration": 1.707
    },
    {
        "text": "you can hear thump, thump, thump, thump,",
        "start": 346.58,
        "duration": 1.769
    },
    {
        "text": "thump, thump, thump, thump, thump, thump",
        "start": 348.35,
        "duration": 1.25
    },
    {
        "text": "BANG ",
        "start": 349.93,
        "duration": 0.819
    },
    {
        "text": "That's what it does.",
        "start": 350.75,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh, that is....",
        "start": 354.02,
        "duration": 1.03
    },
    {
        "text": "That's terrifying",
        "start": 355.33,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "There's one more coming!",
        "start": 357.518,
        "duration": 0.706
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you hear it? Thump, thump, thump.",
        "start": 358.224,
        "duration": 1.096
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah.",
        "start": 359.42,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh, my God.",
        "start": 361.66,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "The anticipation's the worst part.",
        "start": 369.96,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh, my God, you know, it's coming.",
        "start": 371.76,
        "duration": 1.759
    },
    {
        "text": "Huh?",
        "start": 375.36,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "This is how they set up the train, by the way, ",
        "start": 377.82,
        "duration": 1.865
    },
    {
        "text": "they connect all the carriages to each other...",
        "start": 379.86,
        "duration": 2.028
    },
    {
        "text": "they connect them to each other",
        "start": 385.91,
        "duration": 1.359
    },
    {
        "text": "by clamping them together.",
        "start": 388.44,
        "duration": 1.769
    },
    {
        "text": "And the forces are just so immense,",
        "start": 390.81,
        "duration": 2.009
    },
    {
        "text": "they push the train back and forth.",
        "start": 393.23,
        "duration": 1.839
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh, we're moving.",
        "start": 397.078,
        "duration": 0.984
    },
    {
        "text": "We're moving smoothly.",
        "start": 398.062,
        "duration": 0.967
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh, my God. We just missed the police car.",
        "start": 402.12,
        "duration": 2.04
    },
    {
        "text": "We'll just tuck  back down for a minute.",
        "start": 406.56,
        "duration": 1.16
    },
    {
        "text": "To be continued",
        "start": 408.36,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "This is true adventure. ",
        "start": 493.19,
        "duration": 2.285
    },
    {
        "text": "Unpredictable and wild.",
        "start": 495.728,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "You know it when you feel your stomach sinking just a little bit, ",
        "start": 499.153,
        "duration": 3.557
    },
    {
        "text": "when you feel that lump in your throat, ",
        "start": 504.136,
        "duration": 2.063
    },
    {
        "text": "and your heart starts racing,",
        "start": 506.689,
        "duration": 1.826
    },
    {
        "text": "and you think to yourself:",
        "start": 509.798,
        "duration": 1.588
    },
    {
        "text": " it’s impossible. ",
        "start": 512.146,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "And yet, you do it anyway.",
        "start": 514.795,
        "duration": 2.623
    },
    {
        "text": "What's it really like ",
        "start": 525.03,
        "duration": 1.185
    },
    {
        "text": "to cross the Sahara Desert ",
        "start": 526.215,
        "duration": 1.893
    },
    {
        "text": "on a coal train?",
        "start": 528.488,
        "duration": 1.752
    },
    {
        "text": "Well, I think this is one of",
        "start": 530.79,
        "duration": 2.249
    },
    {
        "text": "those once in a lifetime, bucketlist",
        "start": 533.07,
        "duration": 2.162
    },
    {
        "text": "kind of experiences. ",
        "start": 535.232,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "I mean, granted",
        "start": 536.232,
        "duration": 1.938
    },
    {
        "text": "I haven't lasted a single night yet",
        "start": 538.17,
        "duration": 2.009
    },
    {
        "text": "but so far, ",
        "start": 541.02,
        "duration": 1.078
    },
    {
        "text": "this pristine, wild and raw landscape ",
        "start": 542.098,
        "duration": 2.913
    },
    {
        "text": "that I see around me,",
        "start": 545.011,
        "duration": 1.41
    },
    {
        "text": "it's just something else.",
        "start": 546.421,
        "duration": 1.228
    },
    {
        "text": "It's like something out of a different time,",
        "start": 547.65,
        "duration": 1.919
    },
    {
        "text": "a different era, something that would have",
        "start": 549.57,
        "duration": 2.058
    },
    {
        "text": "happened 100 years ago ",
        "start": 551.79,
        "duration": 1.512
    },
    {
        "text": "but not today.",
        "start": 553.302,
        "duration": 1.938
    },
    {
        "text": "It's one of those last remaining experiences",
        "start": 555.24,
        "duration": 2.999
    },
    {
        "text": "that are so truly raw ",
        "start": 558.24,
        "duration": 1.225
    },
    {
        "text": "so truly pristine ",
        "start": 560.52,
        "duration": 1.617
    },
    {
        "text": "and completely unfiltered.",
        "start": 562.137,
        "duration": 2.118
    },
    {
        "text": "This is the real deal!",
        "start": 564.603,
        "duration": 1.319
    },
    {
        "text": "This is the real deal.",
        "start": 567.63,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "And that's why I'm here.",
        "start": 569.61,
        "duration": 1.38
    },
    {
        "text": "That's why we're here.",
        "start": 571.77,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Did you just fly your drone here??",
        "start": 608.825,
        "duration": 1.824
    },
    {
        "text": "Can't believe it!",
        "start": 610.649,
        "duration": 1.161
    },
    {
        "text": "There it is!",
        "start": 615.263,
        "duration": 0.849
    },
    {
        "text": "This is amazing, guys!",
        "start": 617.126,
        "duration": 1.09
    },
    {
        "text": "Starting to get cold.",
        "start": 631.213,
        "duration": 1.02
    },
    {
        "text": "The sun will set in about half an hour.",
        "start": 634.129,
        "duration": 1.871
    },
    {
        "text": "And after that...",
        "start": 637.774,
        "duration": 0.879
    },
    {
        "text": "It's just the dark, deep night.",
        "start": 640.19,
        "duration": 1.229
    },
    {
        "text": "Bread and butter",
        "start": 661.1,
        "duration": 1.35
    },
    {
        "text": "done.",
        "start": 663.62,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "There's literally no way to make anything else.",
        "start": 667.65,
        "duration": 1.889
    },
    {
        "text": "Can't cook here.",
        "start": 670.98,
        "duration": 1.146
    },
    {
        "text": "No restaurant delivery service.",
        "start": 672.84,
        "duration": 1.679
    },
    {
        "text": "Gotta deal with it, huh?",
        "start": 676.61,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "I know this doesn't seem like the most",
        "start": 682.75,
        "duration": 1.859
    },
    {
        "text": "conventional kind of bed.",
        "start": 684.61,
        "duration": 1.609
    },
    {
        "text": "But there's no other choice",
        "start": 687.21,
        "duration": 2.25
    },
    {
        "text": "we gotta make yourself comfortable somehow.",
        "start": 690.06,
        "duration": 1.559
    },
    {
        "text": "So this is what we're doing.",
        "start": 691.65,
        "duration": 1.079
    },
    {
        "text": "Little mat. Mike's got a cushion.",
        "start": 694.5,
        "duration": 2.199
    },
    {
        "text": "A bit of a luxury here... ",
        "start": 697.3,
        "duration": 1.221
    },
    {
        "text": "and two sleeping bags.",
        "start": 700.21,
        "duration": 1.289
    },
    {
        "text": "That's it. This is how we're spending",
        "start": 702.28,
        "duration": 1.649
    },
    {
        "text": "tonight.",
        "start": 703.93,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "That over there, that's not Mike, ",
        "start": 741.93,
        "duration": 1.979
    },
    {
        "text": "Mike's right here.",
        "start": 743.909,
        "duration": 1.331
    },
    {
        "text": "That guy...",
        "start": 746.94,
        "duration": 1.224
    },
    {
        "text": "just climbed into our car,",
        "start": 748.798,
        "duration": 2.12
    },
    {
        "text": "said 'ca va?'",
        "start": 751.456,
        "duration": 0.972
    },
    {
        "text": "and went to sit down there.",
        "start": 752.871,
        "duration": 1.652
    },
    {
        "text": "Unexpected guest.",
        "start": 755.362,
        "duration": 1.059
    },
    {
        "text": "I know it may seem hard to believe, ",
        "start": 757.921,
        "duration": 1.496
    },
    {
        "text": "but this train is used by a handful of locals ",
        "start": 759.417,
        "duration": 2.116
    },
    {
        "text": "for their daily commute to work.",
        "start": 761.533,
        "duration": 1.667
    },
    {
        "text": "Quite different from your standard metro train isn’t it?",
        "start": 763.612,
        "duration": 2.364
    },
    {
        "text": "A day and a night",
        "start": 768.21,
        "duration": 1.576
    },
    {
        "text": "on an iron ore train",
        "start": 770.354,
        "duration": 1.206
    },
    {
        "text": "Bet you guys wanna see",
        "start": 772.281,
        "duration": 0.73
    },
    {
        "text": "what my face actually looks like?",
        "start": 773.011,
        "duration": 1.192
    },
    {
        "text": "I can't see.",
        "start": 779.133,
        "duration": 0.867
    },
    {
        "text": "You tell me!",
        "start": 780.0,
        "duration": 0.876
    },
    {
        "text": "It's breakfast time, finally, ",
        "start": 787.47,
        "duration": 1.761
    },
    {
        "text": "my favourite part of the day.",
        "start": 789.231,
        "duration": 1.429
    },
    {
        "text": "This is what we've got.",
        "start": 791.2,
        "duration": 1.229
    },
    {
        "text": "Beautiful",
        "start": 793.57,
        "duration": 1.114
    },
    {
        "text": "We didn't eat much last night,",
        "start": 794.684,
        "duration": 1.311
    },
    {
        "text": "so we still have pretty much everything",
        "start": 795.995,
        "duration": 1.223
    },
    {
        "text": "that we left with,",
        "start": 797.218,
        "duration": 1.327
    },
    {
        "text": "which is amazing.",
        "start": 798.545,
        "duration": 1.274
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm starving.",
        "start": 800.12,
        "duration": 1.301
    },
    {
        "text": "It's been a long, cold night.",
        "start": 801.421,
        "duration": 1.239
    },
    {
        "text": "I just need to get some food in my belly.",
        "start": 803.357,
        "duration": 1.637
    },
    {
        "text": "This Canadian ",
        "start": 807.7,
        "duration": 1.091
    },
    {
        "text": "maple butter from Mike.",
        "start": 808.791,
        "duration": 1.994
    },
    {
        "text": "I might just eat it before he does...",
        "start": 812.115,
        "duration": 1.894
    },
    {
        "text": "This is my breakfast sandwich.",
        "start": 820.83,
        "duration": 1.229
    },
    {
        "text": "It doesn't look great, ",
        "start": 822.73,
        "duration": 1.138
    },
    {
        "text": "but I'm sure it will taste amazing.",
        "start": 824.306,
        "duration": 1.601
    },
    {
        "text": "And just like that, 24 hours later, ",
        "start": 834.713,
        "duration": 2.369
    },
    {
        "text": "the Sahara cargo express ",
        "start": 837.193,
        "duration": 1.335
    },
    {
        "text": "emerged from the desert, and so did we. ",
        "start": 838.528,
        "duration": 2.602
    },
    {
        "text": "It was hard to believe that the world ",
        "start": 841.795,
        "duration": 1.477
    },
    {
        "text": "was once again becoming quite normal, ",
        "start": 843.272,
        "duration": 1.799
    },
    {
        "text": "quite predictable, ",
        "start": 845.53,
        "duration": 1.129
    },
    {
        "text": "the bittersweet feeling of returning to civilisation ",
        "start": 847.118,
        "duration": 2.602
    },
    {
        "text": "from the depths of the sandy ocean.",
        "start": 850.084,
        "duration": 1.984
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh, my God, I can't believe we've arrived!",
        "start": 859.41,
        "duration": 1.59
    },
    {
        "text": "this guy has been chasing the train ",
        "start": 862.01,
        "duration": 1.439
    },
    {
        "text": "for the last kilometre.",
        "start": 863.449,
        "duration": 1.21
    },
    {
        "text": "I think expecting us to hitch a ride with him.",
        "start": 864.912,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Why do we do this to ourselves?",
        "start": 898.446,
        "duration": 2.058
    },
    {
        "text": "I think it's to feel raw.",
        "start": 906.27,
        "duration": 1.59
    },
    {
        "text": "And real.",
        "start": 909.288,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Feel that power of the elements.",
        "start": 911.84,
        "duration": 2.652
    },
    {
        "text": "Something unfiltered.",
        "start": 915.91,
        "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
        "text": "To get in touch with ourselves ",
        "start": 920.73,
        "duration": 1.504
    },
    {
        "text": "and to feel that we have conquered",
        "start": 922.573,
        "duration": 1.324
    },
    {
        "text": "something within ourselves, ",
        "start": 923.897,
        "duration": 1.284
    },
    {
        "text": "I think that's why we do this.",
        "start": 925.181,
        "duration": 1.849
    },
    {
        "text": "And this is where the journey ends.",
        "start": 929.89,
        "duration": 1.229
    }
]